1{-# LANGUAGE OverloadedStrings #-}
2{-# OPTIONS_GHC -Wall #-}
3{-# OPTIONS_GHC -fno-warn-orphans #-}
4
5module Koshucode.Baala.Writer.Json
6  ( -- * JSON
7    resultJson,
8    termsToJSON,
9    jsonNull,
10    A.ToJSON (..),
11
12    -- * GeoJSON
13    resultGeoJson,
14    ToGeoJSON (..),
15  ) where
16
17import           Data.Aeson                        ((.=))
18import qualified Data.Aeson                        as A
19import qualified Data.ByteString.Lazy              as Byte
20import qualified Data.Text                         as T
21import qualified System.IO                         as IO
22import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Syntax            as S
23import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Data              as D
24import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Core              as C
25
26
27-- --------------------------------------------  JSON
28
29resultJson :: (A.ToJSON c) => C.ResultWriter c
30resultJson = C.ResultWriterJudge "json" hPutJSON
31
32hPutJSON :: (A.ToJSON c) => C.ResultWriterJudge c
33hPutJSON _ _ status [] = return status
34hPutJSON h _ status (j1:js) =
35    do IO.hPutStr h "[ "
36       put j1
37       mapM_ cput js
38       IO.hPutStrLn h "]"
39       return status
40    where
41      put j  = do Byte.hPutStr h $ A.encode j
42                  IO.hPutChar h '\n'
43      cput j = do IO.hPutStr h ", "
44                  put j
45
46instance (A.ToJSON c) => A.ToJSON (D.Judge c) where
47    toJSON (D.JudgeAffirm p xs) =
48        A.object [ "judge" .= text "|--"
49                 , "name"  .= p
50                 , "args"  .= termsToJSON xs ]
51    toJSON _ = undefined
52
53termsToJSON :: (A.ToJSON c) => [S.Term c] -> A.Value
54termsToJSON xs = A.object $ map json xs where
55    json (n, c) = (T.pack n, A.toJSON c)
56
57text :: T.Text -> T.Text
58text s = s
59
60jsonNull :: A.Value
61jsonNull = A.Null
62
63instance A.ToJSON D.BaalaC where
64    toJSON c = case c of
65        D.VCode s      -> A.toJSON s
66        D.VText s      -> A.toJSON s
67        D.VTerm s      -> A.toJSON $ '/' : s
68        D.VDec  n      -> A.toJSON (D.decimalFractional n :: Double)
69        D.VClock t     -> unimplemented t
70        D.VTime t      -> unimplemented t
71        D.VBool b      -> A.toJSON b
72        D.VEmpty       -> jsonNull
73        D.VEnd         -> jsonNull
74        D.VInterp i    -> unimplemented i
75        D.VType t      -> unimplemented t
76        D.VList xs     -> A.toJSON xs
77        D.VSet  xs     -> A.toJSON xs
78        D.VTie  xs     -> termsToJSON xs
79        D.VRel r       -> unimplemented r
80        where unimplemented x = A.toJSON $ "<unimplemented>" ++ show x
81
82
83-- --------------------------------------------  GeoJSON
84
85resultGeoJson :: (A.ToJSON c) => C.ResultWriter c
86resultGeoJson = C.ResultWriterJudge "geojson" hPutGeoJson
87
88hPutGeoJson :: (A.ToJSON c) => C.ResultWriterJudge c
89hPutGeoJson _ _ status [] = return status
90hPutGeoJson h _ status (j1:js) =
91    do IO.hPutStrLn h "{ \"type\": \"FeatureCollection\""
92       IO.hPutStrLn h ", \"crs\": {\"type\": \"name\", \"properties\": {\"name\": \"urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84\"}}"
93       IO.hPutStrLn h ", \"features\": ["
94       IO.hPutStr   h "  "
95       put j1
96       mapM_ cput js
97       IO.hPutStrLn h "]}"
98       return status
99    where
100      put j  = do Byte.hPutStr h $ A.encode $ toGeoJSON j
101                  IO.hPutChar h '\n'
102      cput j = do IO.hPutStr h ", "
103                  put j
104
105class ToGeoJSON a where
106    toGeoJSON :: a -> A.Value
107
108instance (A.ToJSON c) => ToGeoJSON (D.Judge c) where
109    toGeoJSON (D.JudgeAffirm _ xs) =
110        A.object [ "type"       .= text "Feature"
111                 , "properties" .= A.object [ "name" .= name ]
112                 , "geometry"   .= geo ]
113            where name   = lookup "name" xs
114                  lat    = lookup "lat"  xs
115                  long   = lookup "long" xs
116                  geo    = A.object [ "type"        .= text "Point"
117                                    , "coordinates" .= [long, lat]]
118    toGeoJSON _ = undefined
